---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Luda Hex"
  description="About Yianna Paris, the security specialist behind Luda Hex."
>
  <section class="container about">
    <div class="prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">// about</p>
      <h1>Hi, I'm Yianna</h1>
      <p>
        I like to break systems and help others build them securely. 
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm a consultant in Offensive and Application Security. You can find me
        speaking at conferences, training at events such as DEFCON or creating
        security workshops for private company events.
      </p>
      <p>
        My focus areas are an intersection of web and cloud, embedded technologies, 
        hardware and radio devices, wireless protocols, and LLM / Agentic AI apps. 
        I really love agriculture and robotics.
      </p>
      <p>
        My favourite programming language is C, for no other reason than it 
        was the first language I was introduced to that was always called "terrible" —
        and I wanted to learn all the technicalities of why. They told me buffer
        overflows were dead, and then I discovered IoT and embedded software. 
        Telling me it's impossible or too difficult just makes me try harder.
        I am comfortable reading, analysing and quickly getting up to speed in
        almost any tech stack. 
      </p>
      <p>
        I know what it's like to work in a Security Operations Center responding to
        incidents, setting up threat hunting workflows, as well as testing apps 
        and designing secure cloud architecture. It gives me the organisational context
        and empathy needed to help bridge knowledge gaps and find the important problems.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have a Bachelor of Computer Science and a Bachelor of Digital
        Media Design if that matters, it's a creative mix that means I don't 
        really fit in with either group. 
      </p>
      <p>
        Find me on
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/salted-hash/">LinkedIn</a> or
        <a href="https://github.com/nekosoft">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img
      class="mascot"
      src="/images/skull_script_kitty.svg"
      alt=""
      width="200"
      height="200"
    />
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-7);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-block: var(--space-7);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-block: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
  }

  .mascot {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.25));
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .about {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
